description: Warrior Gold Inc. engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral resource properties in Canada. The company primarily explores for gold deposits. It holds a 100% interest in its principal project the Goodfish-Kirana property comprising 29 patented claims with 233 operational cells covering an area of 4,251.54 hectares located in Kirkland Lake, Ontario. The company was formerly known as War Eagle Mining Company Inc. and changed its name to Warrior Gold Inc. in September 2018. Warrior Gold Inc. was incorporated in 1984 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
